original_title: Saving the Great Swamp: Battle to Defeat the Jetport
overview: A new one-hour documentary about the events, people and politics behind the struggle to preserve a rural area of New Jersey between 1959 and 1968. Chronicles the 9-year fight to stop plans to build a huge jetport that threatened towns, wildlife and the aquifer for miles around.
title: Saving the Great Swamp: Battle to Defeat the Jetport
